utservice->cartservice\", \"cartservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"存在显著延迟，特征: high latency spike in requests to ‘redis’\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 1739.742ms，异常耗时 53000.0ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkout operation 显著延迟\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时 2307.623ms，异常耗时 62766.0ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n总之，已支持识别的根因假设集中在 `checkoutservice` 中对 `cartservice` 的请求，以及 `cartservice` 对 `redis` 的访问延迟相关。", "current_hypothesis": "aiops-k8s-08 is the root cause due to node_memory_usage_rate exhaustion, affecting services like cartservice and checkoutservice with latency spikes."}
